<title class="- topic/title ">Scheduling a periodic email report from a station</title>
<shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Configuring the system to periodically email alarm data
from a station to an operator or manager improves the chances that
a human being will pay attention to the alarms and do something about
them.</shortdesc>
<prolog class="- topic/prolog ">
